text:
Alright, let's begin.
The "Alstroemeria Egg Hunt" starts now!

I got one! / I got it.
Got it...!

Oh, it was faster than I thought...
...Wait, everyone only got one, right...

I'm defeated... I was planning to make the prize for
the winner to have me listen to their request...

...Oh, is that so...!
! Then... Tenka-chan, Chiyuki-san, can I have a moment?

Ehehe, Producer-san will listen
to everyone's request one by one!
